---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 129
  - Title: Discourse of Isis to Horus
By: Hermes
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Knowledge Through Chastisement
---
For a refutation, great king, when it has been recognized, brings him who has
been refuted into knowledge of things which he did not know before.
